Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:15.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把我们的村落烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,饶不了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.77,0:00:24.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.67,0:00:50.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.34,0:00:58.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.73,0:01:14.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为阿尔图克伯爵报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,扫平他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.37,0:01:23.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑太子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退分散逃进森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.25,0:01:26.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.63,0:01:37.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们返回城中去帮助提欧阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克永恒不灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不必深追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别动队被魔女干掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.37,0:02:06.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,重整队列准备重新进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这一代似乎成迷宫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,小把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,路被分成了好几条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.47,0:02:30.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是操纵了荆棘时而封路时而开路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是提欧的目的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.07,0:02:37.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他是想迷惑我军让我军分散兵力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真狡猾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总之朝城堡前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,杀过来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来对沙漠的人民来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这魔境之森很不友好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给我下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你单挑决胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚太子米尔扎•库切斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争会赢的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你赶紧离开森林吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到晚上这森林还会变样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,寻求人血的魔物蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就永远躲在城里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,期间我会摧毁所有阿尔图克条约的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,全军撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会攻过来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,特利乌斯・萨博亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然魔法算不上特别厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但军事谋略很突出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.26,0:05:29.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是失算了而是被化解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.56,0:05:37.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下一场战斗就很艰苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.90,0:05:38.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,永夜之森是魔境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,并不适合军队长期驻扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗能用的选项只有两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是率军撤回布鲁塔巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.62,0:06:01.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,离开永夜之森进攻这座城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就正中我方下怀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定要击溃他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.47,0:06:14.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个问题 要不要向南面的莱加里亚派兵呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,向南派兵？为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,向阿尔图克条约的诸国释放信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我军仍兵强马壮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,借此牵制南面的进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是为了引出提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.86,0:06:30.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是提欧敢大摇大摆地走出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就杀回去干掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 立切开始准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.37,0:06:39.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在永夜之森被算计了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.26,0:06:50.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡•梅蕾蒂斯下次可没那么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.52,0:07:01.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,听说米尔扎率领七干士兵准备进攻莱加里亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是无视了我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:08.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎恐怕是想引出提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.86,0:07:09.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.45,0:07:14.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,打算在野外攻击离开森林的我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过这次只能算是敌人的计谋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如今永夜之森的胜利令士气高涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能能放过这个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,借助阿尔图克民众的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,又要率领义勇军啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,碰见米尔扎肯定会被骂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,解放西斯迪纳的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我号召人们揭竿而起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然终结了罗西尼家的统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但有很多人在战争中丧命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.15,0:07:55.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直认为提欧大人能听见人们的心声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而提欧大人能将其转化为语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就率领全军朝独角兽城进发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.22,0:08:17.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克的人们没认可达尔塔尼亚统治是毋庸置疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.93,0:08:25.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛我觉得攻打独角兽城太无谋了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你要真这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就赶紧率军增援阿城图克啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不能选择不离开永夜之森吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在莱加里亚被达尔塔尼亚攻打的期间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人要是毫无行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克的人们便会失望就不会起义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,攻打独角兽城的时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有米尔克离开的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果米尔扎我方军队集结完毕之前赶回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,便会成为一场艰苦的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 只要争取到时间就行了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:08.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就让赛尔杰大人争取这些时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,报告莱加里亚城内举起了白旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.83,0:09:28.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是莱加里亚伯爵及其弟弟伊戈尔子爵弃城而逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.79,0:09:34.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是假装逃跑引诱我们深入的计策呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.47,0:09:37.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,城内已出现暴动和掠夺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,另外我们还捕获了莱加里亚的契约魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是被丢下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,丢下契约魔法师？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真的逃跑了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明明提欧•科尔内罗才刚战胜我军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,赛尔杰・康斯坦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是外号逃亡伯爵的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.16,0:10:04.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这表示对赛尔杰而言提欧根本不是值得信赖的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.75,0:10:08.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,估计把他当成了维拉尔捡回来的流浪君主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总不能置之不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺回城塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.05,0:10:19.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞维斯王拉席克早晚会率领援军杀过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻准备平定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能否给我一周时间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了给我五天搞定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧・科尔內罗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜舍弃莱加里亚一国只为争取时间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来竟然能在短时间内集结这么多士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.22,0:11:08.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子只有煽动民众在行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论对方是多么大的大军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底也只是乌合之众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从正面突击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,将敌人杀个片甲不留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我军在莱加里亚也留有驻兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前只有不到五干人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想对的提欧的军队似乎有将近五万人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.16,0:11:30.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就返回坚固的独角兽城等待援军吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在不利的状况下发 太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.63,0:11:38.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,向瓦尔林德斯达尔克以及本国请求增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,集结到足够兵須再发起决战就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我一仗都不打直接逃回城吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还望您现在先隐忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就相信你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.83,0:12:16.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗率大军包围了独角兽城？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.25,0:12:16.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,此外 阿尔图克条约的所有君主及士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.26,0:12:23.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正渐渐向塞维斯王拉席克的地方聚集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟卢克莱尔伯爵比想象中撑得久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,万一米尔扎阁下被击败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.06,0:12:36.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德便会遭受南北两方的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.27,0:12:40.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我率领三千人的骑士团前去增援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗是危险的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若放任不管很可能成长为庞然大物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到米尔扎阁下的处境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,三干援军会不会稍显不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.12,0:12:58.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟还得提防卢克莱尔伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是最大的努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚本国也会派出增援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,去强烈催促乌尔莉卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.63,0:13:09.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让她这次也派出援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.85,0:13:15.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎那家伙说出那么多大话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,居然落得这幅田地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人来要求了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要我方前去救米尔扎大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等征服了哈曼再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是增援慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的立场就要变差了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,区区哈曼三天拿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿下了斯达尔克还让哈曼进贡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经积攒足够的资金和粮食了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后我要不断夺取领地和爵位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,成为皇帝的人不是马丽娜姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而是父亲埃里克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.43,0:13:59.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来报称诺尔德的舰队正在逼近我国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,进贡了那么多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来居然连领地都要抢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,国库已经空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.36,0:14:13.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,像样的衣服  就只剩丈夫们送我的这件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,索拉斯  约西姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.91,0:14:23.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您爱的男人们  都为我和哈曼殊死而战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.92,0:14:27.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来  似乎要失去一切啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不能下定论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,斯达尔克带了两干上下的奴隶兵来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.60,0:14:40.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说西斯迪纳的从属君主在里面当卧底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,君主做这种“影字”做的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.65,0:14:48.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他是西斯迪纳前领主罗西尼家的当家朱泽尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就跟那位大人配合拉拢奴隶兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说在斯达尔克奴隶的不满情绪日益高涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已是一触即发的状态了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.12,0:15:05.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这时就可以尝试号召斯达尔克的奴隶发动大规模叛乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为此朱泽尔已经安排好了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哈曼可是小国哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算所有奴隶兵都投靠我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得也赢不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我们也应该学习西斯迪纳伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,号召领民奋起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.98,0:15:25.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,领民们也知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅大人是让他们免受掠夺才耗光国库的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.15,0:15:33.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都把我当成了只能这么做的无能君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.45,0:15:38.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从属君主们和士兵们肯定也早就放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅的奔放受到了所有人的仰慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要艾德吉雅大人有所行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必哈曼的人民便会团结一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,与诺尔德的人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,会么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让这一切变得更加实际
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.72,0:16:01.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅大人能否脱下这身衣服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在王城的中庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集着哈曼的从属君主和士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们面前脱下衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再次表明这个国家财富已尽的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们下定决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为保护领地和领民就只有战斗一条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是让我在别人面前脱光？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅大人的身体现在依然极具魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从属君主也好士兵也好领民也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必都会奋起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候要是放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.64,0:16:41.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就无颜面对为我和哈曼而死的丈夫们了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.98,0:16:50.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会一起脱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是穿着衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法让大家下定決心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.69,0:17:26.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.15,0:17:28.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我将一切都献给了诺尔德的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,国库已空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就连能处置的财产都没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.07,0:17:42.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 他们仍想掠夺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想夺走这个国家的领土和人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.12,0:17:50.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过唯独这些是绝对不能拱手让人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.84,0:17:56.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  哪怕要舍弃这仅剩的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.13,0:17:57.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在所不惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,沃妮马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了艾德吉雅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要献上自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,献上生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要跟艾德吉雅大人一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们哈曼的人赢一切都给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是奴隶是万万不会当的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕会丧命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要选择自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,穿成那样说什么大道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,斯达尔克的人民听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.27,0:18:58.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们的故乡即将发生大规模叛乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必再过不久斯达尔克就会被解放吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:07.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经没理由屈服于诺尔德的人民了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么蠢话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才说话的是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,快看哈曼的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是我们斯达尔克人民现在的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都被夺走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无异于裸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.14,0:19:24.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来人让他闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.39,0:19:29.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 女王不惜舍弃性命也要保护自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的战斗对象不该是哈曼的勇士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而是诺尔德的掠夺者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也投靠女王吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给我吹响号角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.87,0:19:48.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把哈曼的军队和奴隶兵全部杀光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,乌尔莉卡大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说斯达尔克全土开始了奴隶起义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.09,0:20:04.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能都  是哈曼女王的胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去我就无颜面对父亲埃里克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,全军撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.77,0:20:15.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,回到船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,返回斯达尔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别擅自决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,援军上哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.00,0:20:43.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人率领三干人的瓦尔林德骑士团正在赶过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一抵达我方就岀城迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样应该就能冲破提欧•科尔内罗的阵型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,工蚁佩特尔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不到一天就造出那种东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还不止如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人驻扎了坚固的阵形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算瓦尔林德边境伯爵前来助阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法轻易会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果马丽娜阁下遭到攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.54,0:21:15.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔塔尼亚本国和乌尔莉卡大人应该也派出援军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联系上了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然打过没有胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还从未输得这么惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.14,0:21:31.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我第一次濒临败北
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而这仅此一次的败北
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会让我失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很可气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.19,0:21:42.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在就只能相信友军会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.29,0:23:19.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞维斯王拉席題军队抵达了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.21,0:23:26.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,兵力约有三万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.87,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.11,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,为了自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.47,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,请退下  如果是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.80,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,那我们就会被断掉退路全灭的
